43
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:46,319
As we get into the text this morning,

44
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:48,279
we really have to deal with some things

45
00:01:48,279 --> 00:01:50,440
from the book of Acts on the book of 1 Corinthians

46
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:52,599
to really set the scene, if you will,

47
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:54,519
